snippet.title: Guild Wars 2: End of Dragons Gameplay Features Trailer
snippet.description: Explore new lands, unlock new ways to play, and take your first steps toward Tyria's future in the third expansion for the award-winning MMORPG Guild Wars 2. Customize your characters' professions with nine new elite specializations, raise your own combat-ready multiplayer siege turtle mount, take your skiff out to reel in a big catch, and more! Pre-purchase today and get bonus items: https://buy.guildwars2.com/
